oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Superman - 1945-02-20
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Episode of radio program Superman, originally broadcast February 20, 1945 by the Mutual Broadcasting System, as recorded by WSIX, Nashville, TN. Featuring Bud Collyer, Jackie Kelk, Jackson Beck (announcer), and Dan McCullough (commercial announcer). Sponsored by Kellogg's Pep cereal.
